(c) instruct the Municipal Assessor and Designated General Services Officer to facilitate the titling of the eight parcels of land in the Municipality name; 

(d) require the designated General Service Officer and Municipal Accountant to 

(i) provide proof of ownership on the two vehicles as identified in audits; and 

